    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road! I've taken good care of it, and it runs like a dream. I'd love for it to go to a good home where it'll be appreciated just as much as I have. Feel free to reach out if you have any questions or want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 29900.0,
