    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s machine, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system. The powertrain is in robust health, with the rod bearings recently addressed for long-term reliability. Power is managed via a precise 6-speed manual gearbox and sent to the rear wheels through the factory variable M differential lock. The chassis has been proactively reinforced at the subframe mounting points to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. While showing minor cosmetic wear consistent with its age, the mechanical vitals\u2014including the cooling system and suspension bushings\u2014are dialed in for immediate, high-performance engagement.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
