    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presented here is a well-maintained vehicle that strikes an ideal balance between performance and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small superficial scuff on the rear passenger door\u2014standard for a vehicle of this age. The alloy wheels are in great shape with no curb rash. Inside, the non-smoker cabin is clean and inviting; the leather seats are supple, showing only light creasing on the driver-side bolster. Every electronic component, from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system, operates exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is robust. It has been serviced at regular intervals, with a recent oil change and brake inspection performed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread life remaining, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. Included with the sale are two sets of keys and a complete folder of service receipts, offering full transparency into its history.",
